{
  "stem": "10862.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't tell you in the story before, but after the Germans had evacuated all the people from the ghetto, my sister, Eda, and I went back into the ghetto, and to the apartments where all the people lived.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whatever we could find of value, we were looting all the homes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'd take silver, kiddish cups, candlesticks, whatever they had, anything of value-- even linen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we would wrap ourselves around with it, put it into our pockets, and we would go back and try to sell it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they'd give it to these people and they would hoping-- we would hope that they would keep us safe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, at that time, we walked right through because the ghetto was pretty much empty.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans, somehow or another, nobody noticed us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody above must have been watching over us because nobody bothered us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just walked through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe at that point, they thought maybe we were two little Gentile little girls, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't bother us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we walked through into the Aryan side, where our other sister was there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saved-- we gave these, all the things that we had to these people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And unfortunately, that same night, this man that we had given everything to him had a little bit too much to drink.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night, he started yelling at us, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] Dirty Jews, get out of here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he started yelling so loud, and he came with a hatchet with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got very, very frightened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So during the middle of the night, my sister-- Hannah, my oldest sister-- grabbed me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we started running in the middle of the night to a cornfield not far away.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
